{"sample_id": "general_037_piwm_4ababbeb60", "source_id": "piwm_4ababbeb60", "domain": "general", "gold_stage": "action", "raw_output": "<stage>action</stage>\n<intent_label>confirm_choice</intent_label>\n<visual_summary>顾客主动走向柜台或服务区域，说明接近明确咨询或决策时刻。 当前场景是腕表柜台，可见判断应围绕顾客是否需要围绕表盘大小、表带材质、上手比例和佩戴场合获得人工确认。视角为导购可观察中近距离视角。</visual_summary>\n<engagement_pattern>顾客从浏览转向服务/结算区域。 移动方向明确，正在接近服务点。</engagement_pattern>\n<gaze_and_attention>视线朝向柜台、导购或服务点。</gaze_and_attention>\n<body_and_hands>身体朝柜台方向前进。 手部可能携带商品、指向柜台或准备询问。</body_and_hands>\n<belief>The shopper may be ready for service, but still needs final confirmation.</belief>\n<desire>confirm the preferred choice</desire>\n<intention>move toward confirming the choice</intention>", "parse_success": true, "predicted_stage": "action", "predicted_intent_label": "confirm_choice", "predicted_belief": "The shopper may be ready for service, but still needs final confirmation.", "predicted_desire": "confirm the preferred choice", "predicted_intention": "move toward confirming the choice", "predicted_observable_evidence": "顾客主动走向柜台或服务区域，说明接近明确咨询或决策时刻。 当前场景是腕表柜台，可见判断应围绕顾客是否需要围绕表盘大小、表带材质、上手比例和佩戴场合获得人工确认。视角为导购可观察中近距离视角。", "predicted_engagement_pattern": "顾客从浏览转向服务/结算区域。 移动方向明确，正在接近服务点。", "predicted_gaze_and_attention": "视线朝向柜台、导购或服务点。", "predicted_body_and_hands": "身体朝柜台方向前进。 手部可能携带商品、指向柜台或准备询问。", "stage_correct": true}
